0.1.0.name: connect20/Buzzthemes_Go_Camping_Template
0.1.0.description: Go Camping template is a responsive Magento template which was created specifically for E-business store systems providing picnic instruments, camping furniture as well as camping clothes. By using a light gamut in tandem with simple natural designs, the Camping Store template helps ease the burden of the installation and application of itself significantly.

suggest.magento-hackathon\/magento-composer-inst: Allows to manage this package as a dependency
